	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is there any Famicom devcard readily available? I want something bare-bones that allows to put a custom circuit on it.<br /><br />If there isn't any, I'll start a new thread with a poll to know who will be interested to have one, because in that case I'll design one. &quot;Design&quot; is a broad term as it will be bare-bones as I want it, that is, a very simple prototyping PCB that you can plug in a Famicom with card pins properly labeled, and indicator of the front of the card (to potentially mitigate the possibility of plugging in the wrong way).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


